div.div:
Create WHAMR CSV
sample rate = 16K
set_type = [tr, cv, tt]
mix_both = mix_single_reverb
s1 = s1_anechoic (tr) | s1 = s1_reverb (tr)
s2 = s2_anechoic (tr) | s2 = s2_reverb (tr)
It creates three csv files each for train, cv and test containing id, duration, mix wav path, s1 wav path, s2 wav path, noise wav path.
